Codeforces Problem : https://codeforces.com/contest/1343/problem/D

Constant Palindrome Problem:
-------------------------------------------------------------
solution:
-----------
It is obvious that if we fix the value of ğ‘¥ then there are three cases for the pair of elements:

We don't need to change anything in this pair;
we can replace one element to fix this pair;
we need to replace both elements to fix this pair.
The first part can be calculated easily in ğ‘‚(ğ‘›+ğ‘˜), we just need to create the array of frequencies ğ‘ğ‘›ğ‘¡, where ğ‘ğ‘›ğ‘¡ğ‘¥ is the number of such pairs (ğ‘ğ‘–,ğ‘ğ‘›âˆ’ğ‘–+1) that ğ‘ğ‘–+ğ‘ğ‘›âˆ’ğ‘–+1=ğ‘¥.

The second part is a bit tricky but still doable in ğ‘‚(ğ‘›+ğ‘˜). For each pair, let's understand the minimum and the maximum sum we can obtain using at most one replacement. For the ğ‘–-th pair, all such sums belong to the segment [ğ‘šğ‘–ğ‘›(ğ‘ğ‘–,ğ‘ğ‘›âˆ’ğ‘–+1)+1;ğ‘šğ‘ğ‘¥(ğ‘ğ‘–,ğ‘ğ‘›âˆ’ğ‘–+1)+ğ‘˜]. Let's make +1 on this segment using prefix sums (make +1 in the left border, âˆ’1 in the right border plus one and then just compute prefix sums on this array). Let this array be ğ‘ğ‘Ÿğ‘’ğ‘“. Then the value ğ‘ğ‘Ÿğ‘’ğ‘“ğ‘¥ tells the number of such pairs that we need to replace at most one element in this pair to make it sum equals ğ‘¥.

And the last part can be calculated as ğ‘›2âˆ’ğ‘ğ‘Ÿğ‘’ğ‘“ğ‘¥. So, for the sum ğ‘¥ the answer is (ğ‘ğ‘Ÿğ‘’ğ‘“ğ‘¥âˆ’ğ‘ğ‘›ğ‘¡ğ‘¥)+(ğ‘›2âˆ’ğ‘ğ‘Ÿğ‘’ğ‘“ğ‘¥)â‹…2. We just need to take the minimum such value among all possible sums from 2 to 2ğ‘˜.

There is another one solution that uses scanline, not depends on ğ‘˜ and works in ğ‘‚(ğ‘›logğ‘›) but it has no cool ideas to explain it here (anyway the main idea is almost the same as in the solution above).


Program:
--------------------------------------------------
#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
#define ll long long int
#define ld long double
#define m 1000000
#define mod         1000000007
#define rep(i,a,b)	for(ll  i=a;i<b;i++)
#define repi(i,a,b)	for(ll  i=a;i<=b;i++)
#define per(i,a,b)  for(ll i=a;i>=b;i--)

int main()
{
    ll t;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--){
        ll n,k,ans=mod;
        cin>>n>>k;
        ll arr[n];
        rep(i,0,n)
        cin>>arr[i];
        ll freq[(2*k)+2]={0};
        for(ll i=0;i<n/2;i++)
        freq[arr[i]+arr[n-i-1]]++;
        ll prefix[2*k + 2]={0};
        for(ll i=0;i<n/2;i++){
            prefix[min(arr[i],arr[n-i-1])+1]++;
            prefix[max(arr[i],arr[n-i-1])+k+1]--;
        }//for
        for(ll i=1;i<=(2*k)+1;i++){
            prefix[i]+=prefix[i-1];
        }//for
         for(ll i=2;i<=(2*k);i++){
             ans = min(ans,(prefix[i]-freq[i])+((n/2) - prefix[i])*2 );
         }//for
         cout<<ans<<endl;
    }//while
return 0;
}
